Variable Kairos_partial_dete1
Title: Kairos partial detection correction all sites for transition point
Description: Partial detection correction for all sites for the sub-analysis for selecting the transition point.
Definition: IF Partial_detect_metho='Linear'~
	THEN IF (Full_distribution_s2 <= Aerial_min_detected_)~
		THEN 0~
	ELSE Partial_detection_c9~
ELSE IF Partial_detect_metho='Binned'~
	THEN Partial_detection_c9[@Selected_emission_in=@Well_site_coverage - Size(Well_site_coverage) +Size(Selected_emission_in), defVal:0]~
ELSE Null
NodeLocation: 96,232,1
NodeSize: 80,48
WindState: 2,682,-4,720,350
ValueState: 2,1,82,546,399,1,MIDM
{!50000|Att_ColumnWidths: [63]}

Variable Partial_detection_10
Title: Partial detection correction all sites for transition point
Description: The partial detection correction for all sites for computing the transition point
Definition: IF (Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian') OR (Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett')~
	THEN Kairos_partial_dete1~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='California'~
	THEN 0~
ELSE Null
NodeLocation: 96,360,1
NodeSize: 80,48

Variable Plume_partial_detec1
Title: Plume partial detection correction multiplicative for transition point
Units: %
Description: Multiplier for plume-level emissions in the partial detect range to compute additional emissions not detected (does not include original emissions).~
For computing the transition point.
Definition: IF (Partial_detection_10 > 0)~
		THEN (1/Partial_detection_10 - 1)~
ELSE 0
NodeLocation: 272,360,1
NodeSize: 80,48
WindState: 2,558,242,720,350
ValueState: 2,875,466,1150,451,0,MIDM
ReformVal: [Null,Well_site_coverage]
Att__TotalsIndex: [Well_site_coverage]

Variable Full_cumsum_partial5
Title: Full cumsum partial detection correction for transition point.
Units: kgh
Description: Cumulative partial detection correction computed for calculating the transition point (min aerial emission to include).~
For computing the transition point.
Definition: Cumulate(Partial_detection_c8, Well_site_coverage)
NodeLocation: 624,480,1
NodeSize: 80,48
WindState: 2,32,104,720,350
ValueState: 2,767,241,911,359,0,MEAN
Aliases: Alias Al1753574691
GraphSetup: Att_GraphValueRange Full_distribution_so:1,,1,,,,,7956.570565700531,9113.429546356201,0~
Att_GraphValueRange Full_cumsum_partial5:1,,1,,,,,0,100M,0
ReformVal: [Well_site_coverage,Well_site_coverage,Undefined,Undefined,Undefined,2]
Att__TotalsIndex: [Well_site_coverage]
Att_XRole: Well_site_coverage
Att_ExogenousValues: [Log_full_distributio]
{!40600|Att_ClusterIndex: Run}

Variable Partial_detection_c8
Title: Partial detection correction by plume for transition point.
Units: kgh
Description: Computed additional emissions not detected (does not include original emissions).~
For computing the transition point.
Definition: Plume_partial_detec1*Full_distribution_s2
NodeLocation: 448,360,1
NodeSize: 80,48
WindState: 2,518,84,720,350
ValueState: 2,1483,456,416,303,,MEAN
Att__TotalsIndex: [Well_site_coverage]

Variable Total_partial_detec3
Title: Total partial detection correction for transition point.
Units: kgh
Description: Total partial detection correction for computing transition point.
Definition: Sum(Partial_detection_c8, Well_site_coverage)
NodeLocation: 448,480,1
NodeSize: 80,48
ValueState: 2,1491,82,416,303,,MEAN

Variable Full_distribution_s2
Title: Full distribution sort using min detected
Description: Uses min detected emission as the crossover point between Rutherford & aerial emissions.
