Variable Joint_Rutherford_aer
Title: Joint Rutherford aerial distribution using min detected
Units: kgh
Description: Joint simulated + aerially measured distribution transitioning at the minimum aerially detected emission instead of at a higher transition point.
Definition: IF (Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian') OR (Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett')~
	THEN IF @Well_site_coverage <= Size(Selected_emission_in)~
		THEN Quantified_emission2[@Selected_emission_in=@Well_site_coverage]~
	ELSE Rutherford_sample_be~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='California'~
	THEN IF @Well_site_coverage <= Size(Duren_O_G_productio1)~
		THEN Duren_O_G_prod_plume[@Duren_O_G_productio1=@Well_site_coverage]~
	ELSE Rutherford_sample_be~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='CM'~
	THEN IF @Well_site_coverage <= Number_of_aerial_emi~
		THEN Aerial_production_em~
	ELSE Rutherford_sample_be
