Variable Emissions_larger_th1
Title: Emissions larger than min aerial detect and smaller than Max Rutherford array
Description: Emissions from aerial detections and partial detection uisng a smaller index that includes only emissions between the smallest aerially detected emission and the largest simulated emission.~
For computing the transition point.
Definition: FOR jj := Run DO BEGIN~
	Full_distribution_s2*(Full_distribution_s2 >= Aerial_min_detected_[Run=jj])*(Full_distribution_s2[Run=jj] <= Max_Rutherford_emiss)~
END~
{Subset((Full_distribution_s2[Run=1] >= Aerial_min_detected_[Run=1])*(Full_distribution_s2[Run=1] <= Max_Rutherford_emiss));}
