Variable Aerial_min_detected_
Title: Aerial min detected emission
Units: kgh
Description: The smallest emission quantified in a given survey.
Definition: IF (Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian') OR (Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett')~
	THEN Min_Kairos_detected_~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='California'~
	THEN Duren_min_detected_a~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='CM'~
	THEN Duren_min_detected_s~
ELSE Null
