Variable Min_Kairos_detected_
Title: Min Kairos-detected emission kgh
Units: kgh
Description: The smallest emission detected by Kairos in the selected campaign.~
Uses estimated emission rates before accounting for uncertainty and calibrating based on controlled releases.
Definition: IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian'~
	THEN Min(Kairos_Permian_all_e, Kairos_Permian_plu10, ignoreNonNumbers:True)~
{Min(Average(Quantified_emission2, Run), Selected_emission_in)}~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett'~
	THEN Min(Kairos_Barnett_plum3[Kairos_Barnett_plum4='emission_rate_kgh'], Kairos_Barnett_plume)~
ELSE Null
NodeLocation: 104,168,1
NodeSize: 72,40
WindState: 2,1205,53,720,350
ValueState: 2,1496,251,416,303,,SAMP

Variable Duren_min_detected_s
Title: Duren min detected selected campaign plume kgh
Units: kgh
Description: Min emission detected at any site (oil and gas or not) by a Carbon Mapper campaign.~
Uses emissions pre-quantification uncertainty adjustment.
Definition: INDEX nonzeros := Subset(Selected_CM_plumes[CM_plume_field='qplume']>0);~
Min(Selected_CM_plumes[CM_plume_field='qplume', Selected_CM_plume_ac=nonzeros], nonzeros, ignoreNonNumbers:True)~
{IF Include_repeats_in_w='Yes'~
	THEN INDEX nonzeros := Subset(Selected_CM_OG_prod1[CM_plume_field='qplume']>0);~
			Min(Selected_CM_OG_prod1[CM_plume_field='qplume', Selected_CM_plume_OG=nonzeros], nonzeros, ignoreNonNumbers:True)~
ELSE IF Include_repeats_in_w='No'~
	THEN Min_aerial_emission1~
ELSE Null}
