Variable Full_CDF_remove_zero
Title: Full CDF remove zero emissions
Description: All relevant well site (production) cumulative distribution functions from the paper.~
Includes an option to removes sites with zero emissions to save space (these are accounted or in post-processing in Python).~
Fields are:~
Emission magnitude for each site~
Log10 of emission magnitude for each site~
Cumulative emissions by site~
Cumulative aerially measured emissions~
Cumulative emissions implied in the partial detection range~
Cumulative simulated emissions~
Log10 of cumulative simulated emissions~
Cumulative aerially measured emissions~
Simulated site-level emission magnitude (using the Rutherford et al. model), including sites above the transition point.~
Cumulative emissions fraction, including simulated, aerial, and partial detect emissions.~
Cumultive emissions fraction considering only simulated emissions, excluding those above the transition point.~
Cumulative emissions fraction from aerially measured emissions above the transition point.~
Cumulative emissions fraction from partial detection above the transition point.~
Log10 of simulated site-level emission magnitude (using the Rutherford et al. model), including sites above the transition point.~
Cumulative fraction of sites/site visits~
Cumulative fraction of sites/site visits, incorporating sites implied by the partial detection correction~
Log10 of cumulative fraction of sites~
Fraction of sites emitting at or above a given emission level, using site-level emissions from the main analysis.~
Fraction of aerially detected sites above the transition point emitting at or above a given level, using site-level emissions from the main analysis. ~
Cumulative fraction of missed sites implied by the partial detection correction.~
The partial detection correction for each simulated site, as a multiplier for measured emissions.
Definition: IF Fractional_CDF_field='Emission magnitude [kgh]'~
	THEN Full_CDF[CDF_field='Emission magnitude [kgh]', Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Log emission magnitude [log(kgh)]'~
	THEN Log_full_distributio[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative emissions [kgh]'~
	THEN (Cumulative_emissions - Full_cumsum_correcte)[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative aerial emissions [kgh]'~
	THEN Aerial_cumulative_e7[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative partial emissions [kgh]'~
	THEN (Total_partial_detect - Full_cumsum_partial1)[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative simulated emissions [kgh]'~
	THEN Rutherford_cumulativ[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Log cumulative emissions'~
	THEN Log_cumulative_emiss[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative aerial emissions [kgh]'~
	THEN (1 - Cumulative_emission_)[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Emission magnitude Rutherford [kgh]'~
	THEN Rutherford_productio[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative emissions fraction [%]'~
	THEN (1 - Cumulative_emission_)[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative emissions fraction Rutherford [%]'~
	THEN Rutherford_below_ae1[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative emissions fraction aerial [%]'~
	THEN Aerial_cumulative_f1[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative emissions fraction partial [%]'~
	THEN Partial_detect_cumul[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Log emission magnitude Rutherford [kgh]'~
	THEN Log_Rutherford_produ[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative fraction of sites'~
	THEN Cumulative_fraction1[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative fraction of sites inc partial detect'~
	THEN Cumulative_fraction_[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Log cumulative fraction of sites'~
	THEN Log_well_site_covera[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Fraction of sites emitting at or above this level'~
	THEN 1 - CumProbability_of_em[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Fraction of aerial detect sites at or above this level'~
	THEN Reverse_cumulative_1[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Cumulative fraction missed partial detect sites'~
	THEN Reverse_cumulative_f[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE IF Fractional_CDF_field='Partial detection correction [%]'~
	THEN Plume_partial_detect[Well_site_coverage=Well_site_coverage_w]~
ELSE Null
