Module CDF_components_for_e
Title: CDF components for export
Description: Components of exported cumulative distribution functions for production sites (well sites).
Author: Evan Sherwin~
Stanford University
Date: Thu, Aug 3, 2023 7:30 AM
NodeLocation: 280,256,1
NodeSize: 72,40
DiagState: 2,45,42,1017,697,17,10

Variable Cumulative_fraction_
Title: Cumulative fraction of sites accounting for partial detection
Description: Adds "missed sites" to the distribution to correspond to the partial detection correction.~
Re-normalizes the cumulative fraction to 1.
Definition: Cumulate((1/Total_well_site_cove)*(1 + Plume_partial_detect), Well_site_coverage)/Sum((1/Total_well_site_cove)*(1 + Plume_partial_detect), Well_site_coverage)
NodeLocation: 440,64,1
NodeSize: 72,40
WindState: 2,352,16,720,350
ValueState: 2,1044,175,738,458,1,MIDM

Variable Log_well_site_covera
Title: Log well site coverage cumulative count
Description: The logarithm of the cumulative count of well sites covered in the selected campaign.
Definition: LogTen(Reverse(Cumulative_fraction_, Well_site_coverage))
NodeLocation: 608,64,1
NodeSize: 72,40
WindState: 2,544,170,720,350

Variable Log_cumulative_emiss
