Variable Midstream_CDF_for_ex
Title: Midstream CDF for export
Description: The full CDF of measured midstream emissions to export.~
Includes detected emission magnitude, as well as cumulative aerially detected and partially detect emissions, both in total and as a fraction of the total.
Definition: IF Midstream_CDF_field='Emission magnitude [kgh]'~
	THEN Source_level_midstr3[Emission_component='Aerial survey']~
ELSE IF Midstream_CDF_field='Cumulative aerial emissions [kgh]'~
	THEN Source_level_cumula2[Emission_component='Aerial survey']~
ELSE IF Midstream_CDF_field='Cumulative partial emissions [kgh]'~
	THEN Source_level_cumula2[Emission_component='Partial detection correction']~
ELSE IF Midstream_CDF_field='Cumulative aerial emissions fraction [%]'~
	THEN Source_level_cumula1[Emission_component='Aerial survey']~
ELSE IF Midstream_CDF_field='Cumulative partial emissions fraction [%]'~
	THEN Source_level_cumula1[Emission_component='Partial detection correction']~
ELSE Null
