Variable Total_aerially_meas1
Title: Total aerially measured emissions 95% snapshot CI
Units: kg/hr
Description: Total aerially measured emissions included in the study.~
Does not include production emissions below the transition point.~
95% confidence interval is for a single Monte Carlo iteration, generally representing a single snapshot measurement of each covered asset.
Definition: IF Mean_CI='Mean'~
	THEN Mean(Sample(Total_aerially_measu), Run)~
ELSE IF Mean_CI='P2.5'~
	THEN GetFract(Sample(Total_aerially_measu), 0.025)~
ELSE IF Mean_CI='P97.5'~
	THEN GetFract(Sample(Total_aerially_measu), 0.975)
