Variable Selected_midstream_a
Title: Selected midstream/all source coverages
Description: Midstream/all-source coverage counts for the selected campaign.
Definition: IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian' ~
	THEN Kairos_Permian_cove1~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett'~
	THEN Kairos_Barnett_cove2~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='California'~
	THEN Duren_midstream_sour~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='CM'~
	THEN CM_selected_OG_midst~
ELSE Null
