Definition: 1..Max_midstream_covera
NodeLocation: 344,280,1
NodeSize: 96,40
WindState: 2,602,127,720,350
ValueState: 2,292,298,416,303,,MIDM

Chance Plume_number_random1
Title: Plume number random draws by source midstream
Description: Randomly selects a coverage of each emission source, including coverages with no detections, based on the total number of overpasses of each source.
Definition: IF Selected_midstream_a=0~
	THEN 0~
ELSE Midstream_source_cov[Midstream_source_cov=Uniform(1, Selected_midstream_a, integer:True), defVal:0]
