Variable Kairos_Barnett_cove2
Title: Kairos Barnett coverage by emitting midstream source
Description: Midstream source coverage counts from the Kairos Barnett campaign.~
Pipelines do not have a coverage count listed.~
We assume here that the number of coverages equals the number of detections (i.e. full persistence).
Definition: VAR init := Kairos_Barnett_sour2[@Kairos_Barnett_sourc=@Kairos_Barnett_sour4, Kairos_Barnett_sour1='Coverage_Count'][Kairos_Barnett_sour4=Kairos_Barnett_emit1];~
IF init='NA'~
	THEN Kairos_Barnett_sour2[@Kairos_Barnett_sourc=@Kairos_Barnett_sour4, Kairos_Barnett_sour1='Detection_Count'][Kairos_Barnett_sour4=Kairos_Barnett_emit1]~
ELSE init
