Index Kairos_Permian_midst
Title: Kairos Permian midstream plume indicator
Description: Excludes well sites. The rest is midstream because Kairos does not generally report emissions from non-oil and gas sites and there are not many other methane sources in the New Mexico Permian.
Definition: Subset((Kairos_source_type_d<>'Well site') AND Kairos_source_type_d)~
