Chance Percent_residual_Ka1
Title: Percent residual Kairos Permian midstream
Description: Compute percent residuals for each midstream plume based on controlled releases from the Chen, Sherwin et al. 2022.
Definition: IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian'~
	THEN IF Controlled_release_a='Logarithmic'~
			THEN Normal(Kairos_calibration_m[Kairos_Permian_midst=Kairos_Permian_midst], Kairos_calibration_S)~
		ELSE IF Controlled_release_a='Linear'~
			THEN Normal(0[Kairos_Permian_midst=Kairos_Permian_midst], Kairos_calibration_1)~
		ELSE IF Controlled_release_a='None'~
			THEN 0~
		ELSE Null~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett'~
	THEN IF Controlled_release_a='Logarithmic'~
			THEN Normal(Kairos_calibration_m[Kairos_Barnett_midst=Kairos_Barnett_midst], Kairos_calibration_S)~
		ELSE IF Controlled_release_a='Linear'~
			THEN Normal(0[Kairos_Barnett_midst=Kairos_Barnett_midst], Kairos_calibration_1)~
		ELSE IF Controlled_release_a='None'~
			THEN 0~
		ELSE Null~
ELSE Null
