Variable Kairos_Permian_mids6
Title: Kairos Permian midstream controlled release adjusted mean
Units: kg(CH4)/hr
Description: Adjust mean emissions for each midstream plume from the Kairos Permian campaign based on controlled releases, as in Chen, Sherwin et al. 2022.~
If linear fit, assumes measurements are unbiased.
Definition: IF Controlled_release_a='Logarithmic'~
	THEN Kairos_log_calibrati*(Kairos_Permian_plum6[Fields_from_Permian_='wind_independent_emission_rate_kghmps']*Kairos_Permian_plum6[Fields_from_Permian_='wind_mps'])^Kairos_log_calibrat1~
ELSE IF Controlled_release_a='Linear'~
	THEN Kairos_linear_calibr*Kairos_Permian_plum6[Fields_from_Permian_='wind_independent_emission_rate_kghmps']*Kairos_Permian_plum6[Fields_from_Permian_='wind_mps']~
ELSE IF Controlled_release_a='None'~
	THEN Kairos_Permian_plum6[Fields_from_Permian_='wind_independent_emission_rate_kghmps']*Kairos_Permian_plum6[Fields_from_Permian_='wind_mps']~
ELSE Null~
{IF Controlled_release_a='Logarithmic'~
	THEN Kairos_log_calibrati*(Kairos_Permian_plum6[Plume_fields_Yulia='emission_rate_kghmps']*Kairos_Permian_plum6[Plume_fields_Yulia='HRRR_mps'])^Kairos_log_calibrat1~
ELSE IF Controlled_release_a='Linear'~
	THEN Kairos_linear_calibr*Kairos_Permian_plum6[Plume_fields_Yulia='emission_rate_kghmps']*Kairos_Permian_plum6[Plume_fields_Yulia='HRRR_mps']~
ELSE IF Controlled_release_a='None'~
	THEN Kairos_Permian_plum6[Plume_fields_Yulia='emission_rate_kghmps']*Kairos_Permian_plum6[Plume_fields_Yulia='HRRR_mps']~
ELSE Null}
