Variable Kairos_Barnett_wind_
Title: Kairos Barnett wind-normalized midstream plumes
Units: kgh/mps
Description: Wind-normalized emission rate for midstream plumes from the Kairos Barnett campaign.~
Uses measured emission rate divided by estimated wind speed for consistency with our partial detection characterization in Sherwin, Chen et al. 2021.
Definition: Kairos_Barnett_vali1[Kairos_Barnett_plum4='emission_rate_kgh']/Kairos_Barnett_vali1[Kairos_Barnett_plum4='wind_speed']
