Variable Kairos_wind_normaliz
Title: Kairos wind-normalized midstream plumes
Units: kgh/mps
Description: Wind-normalized midstream plume emission rates from the selected Kairos campaign.
Definition: IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian'~
	THEN Kairos_Permian_plum6[Fields_from_Permian_='wind_independent_emission_rate_kghmps']~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett'~
	THEN Kairos_Barnett_wind_~
ELSE Null~
{IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian'~
	THEN Kairos_Permian_plum6[Plume_fields_Yulia='emission_rate_kghmps']~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett'~
	THEN Kairos_Barnett_wind_~
ELSE Null}
