Index Selected_CM_plume_m1
Title: Selected CM plume midstream
Description: Midstream plumes identified by Carbon Mapper in the selected campaign after accounting for the possibility of restricting the campaign region to the Midland or Delaware survey areas of the Fall 2021 Permian campaign.
Definition: IF Selected_campaign='Midland_2019_F2021_bounds'~
	THEN CopyIndex(CM_midstream_plumes_)~
ELSE IF Selected_campaign='Delaware_2019_F2021_bounds'~
	THEN CopyIndex(CM_midstream_plumes1)~
ELSE CopyIndex(Selected_CM_plume_mi)~
~
{INDEX init := IF Include_only_Permian='Yes'~
	THEN Subset((CM_plume_campaign='P - Permian_2019') AND (CM_plumes_with_sourc[CM_plume_field='Basin']=Select_CM_basin) AND (CM_plumes_with_sourc[CM_plume_field='ipcc']='Oil & Gas Production'))~
	ELSE Subset((CM_plume_campaign=Select_CM_campaign) AND (CM_plumes_with_sourc[CM_plume_field='Basin']=Select_CM_basin) AND (CM_plumes_with_sourc[CM_plume_field='ipcc']='Oil & Gas Production'));~
~
IF Include_only_Permian='Yes'~
	THEN CopyIndex(Subset(Sum(init=Permian_2019_plumes1, init)))~
ELSE IF Include_only_Permian='No'~
	THEN CopyIndex(init)~
ELSE Null}
NodeLocation: 448,128,1
NodeSize: 72,32
WindState: 2,309,175,720,350
{!40300|Att_SlicerPopupSize: 227,16}

