Module Sort_and_cumulate_se
Title: Sort and cumulate selected emissions
Description: Sort selected emissions and compute cumulative emissions.
Author: evands
Date: Sat, Oct 15, 2022 7:45 AM
NodeLocation: 96,168,1
NodeSize: 72,40
DiagState: 2,238,176,675,327,17,10

Variable Plume_level_aerial_e
Title: Plume-level aerial emissions consistent index
Description: Aerially detected emissions with a dummy index that works for all campaigns.~
Sorted from largest to smallest emission magnitude.
Definition: IF (Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian') OR (Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett')~
	THEN IF @Dummy_plume_consiste <= Size(Selected_emission_in)~
		THEN Quantified_emission2[@Selected_emission_in=@Dummy_plume_consiste]~
	ELSE Null~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='California'~
	THEN IF @Dummy_plume_consiste <= Size(Duren_O_G_productio1)~
		THEN Duren_O_G_prod_plume[@Duren_O_G_productio1=@Dummy_plume_consiste]~
	ELSE Null~
ELSE IF Selected_datasource='CM'~
	THEN IF @Dummy_plume_consiste <= Number_of_aerial_emi~
		THEN Aerial_production_em[@Well_site_coverage=@Dummy_plume_consiste]~
	ELSE Null
NodeLocation: 96,152,1
NodeSize: 72,40
WindState: 2,75,37,720,350
ValueState: 2,185,349,416,303,,MIDM
Aliases: Alias Al399357859
Att__TotalsIndex: [Dummy_plume_consiste]

Variable Aerial_average_emis1
Title: Aerial average emissions consistent index
