Module Source_level_plume_2
Title: Source-level plume IDs for simulated campaign
Description: For each Monte Carlo iteration, select at most one plume identifier for each source identified during the seleted campaign.~
For sources measured multiple times, this is a random draw from all measurements at that source during the selected campaign, including measurements without a detection.~
These are then translated into emission rates.
