Module Rutherford_million_s
Title: Rutherford million site emissions per basin
Description: 1 million simulated site-level emissions, randomly sampled from a simulation of the full basin for alll six basins included in this study.~
All simulations are based on data for 2020. For campaigns conducted in different years, we correct for any differences between the productivity characteristics of the surveyed wells and the basin-wide numbers in the 2020 simulations.~
We do not correct for any changes that may occur over time independent of changes in well site-level gas productivity.~
Data initially imported on September 9, 2022 and subsampled to 1 million site-level emissions estimates per basin on September 17, 2022.
Author: evands
Date: Thu, Sep 8, 2022 11:04 AM
NodeLocation: 472,160,1
NodeSize: 80,40
DiagState: 2,88,25,591,462,19,10,

Variable Selected_Rutherford9
Title: Selected Rutherford site-level emissions 20220917
Units: kg/d
Description: Site-level emissions in the selected basin.~
Currently assumes all basins are like the Permian except those in CA, which are assumed to be like the San Joaquin.
Definition: IF Rutherford_site_leve='National'~
	THEN Rutherford_US_site_l[@Rutherford_national2=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
ELSE IF Rutherford_site_leve='Basin-specific'~
	THEN IF (Selected_datasource='Kairos Permian')~
		THEN Rutherford_Permian15[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_Permian16=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
	ELSE IF (Selected_datasource='Kairos Barnett')~
		THEN Rutherford_Fort_Wo16[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_Fort_Wo15=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
	ELSE IF Selected_datasource='California'~
		THEN Rutherford_San_Joa16[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_San_Joa17=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
	ELSE IF Selected_datasource='CM'~
		THEN IF (Selected_basin='San Joaquin basin') OR (Selected_basin='Los Angeles basin') OR (Selected_basin='Ventura basin') OR (Selected_basin='Sacramento basin')~
			THEN Rutherford_San_Joa16[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_San_Joa17=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
		ELSE IF Selected_basin='Appalachian basin (eastern overthrust area)'~
			THEN Rutherford_Appalac17[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_Appalac16=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
		ELSE IF Selected_basin='Denver basin'~
			THEN Rutherford_Denver_5[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_Denver_I5=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
		ELSE IF Selected_basin='Uinta basin'~
			THEN Rutherford_Uinta_5[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_Uinta_In5=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
		ELSE IF Selected_basin='Permian basin'~
			THEN Rutherford_Permian15[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_Permian16=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
		ELSE IF Selected_basin='Fort Worth basin'~
			THEN Rutherford_Fort_Wo16[Rutherford_field_202='Site emissions [kg/d]', @Rutherford_Fort_Wo15=@Rutherford_site_ind1]~
		ELSE Null~
ELSE Null
