Variable Rutherford_simulat13
Title: Rutherford simulated by percentile
Units: kg/hr
Description: Productivity-stratified simulated emissions from the Rutherford model matching the productivity characteristics of the selected campaign.~
Collates simulated emissions by basin-wide production decile.~
Sets any straggling values to zero (e.g. due to rounding issues in defining deciles, usually 1-2 sites).
Definition: IF Well_site_coverage <= Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=10%]~
	THEN Rutherford_simulate2[Sites_covered_first_=Well_site_coverage, defVal:0]~
ELSE IF Well_site_coverage <= Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=20%]~
	THEN Rutherford_simulate4[Sites_covered_second=Well_site_coverage - Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=10%], defVal:0]~
ELSE IF Well_site_coverage <= Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=30%]~
	THEN Rutherford_simulate5[Sites_covered_third_=Well_site_coverage - Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=20%], defVal:0]~
ELSE IF Well_site_coverage <= Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=40%]~
	THEN Rutherford_simulate6[Sites_covered_fourth=Well_site_coverage - Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=30%], defVal:0]~
ELSE IF Well_site_coverage <= Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=50%]~
	THEN Rutherford_simulate7[Sites_covered_fifth_=Well_site_coverage - Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=40%], defVal:0]~
ELSE IF Well_site_coverage <= Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=55%]~
	THEN Rutherford_simulat29[Sites_covered_55th_p=Well_site_coverage - Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=50%], defVal:0]~
~
~
ELSE IF Well_site_coverage <= Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=60%]~
	THEN Rutherford_simulate8[Sites_covered_sixth_=Well_site_coverage - Covered_well_sites_b[Quantile_to_simulate=55%], defVal:0]~
