Module Stratify_Rutherford1
Title: Stratify Rutherford sites by productivity of covered sites
Description: Stratify simulated emissions from the Rutherford et al. model for the selected basin to match the productivity characteristics of the surveyed region in the selected campaign.~
If the campaign surveys a higher proportion of  high-productivity well sites than the basin at large, this stratification reflects that.
Author: Evan Sherwin~
Stanford University
Date: Tue, Aug 8, 2023 4:01 PM
NodeLocation: 312,272,1
NodeSize: 88,40
DiagState: 2,0,0,870,474,17,10

Module Rutherford_site_ind4
Title: Rutherford site indexes by decile
Description: Identify sites in the selected basin that fall into selected percentile tranches of that basin simulated in Rutherford et al.~
E.g. If 1000 sites in the basin in question fall within the second decile of well site productivity in that basin, those 1000 sites will be seleted in the "Rutherford sites second decile" index.
