Variable Covered_well_site_qu
Title: Covered well site quantiles by Rutherford productivity quantile
Units: mcf/site/day
Description: The number of wells covered in the campaign in each productivity quantile in the basin as a whole (from the Rutherford et al. well site-level numbers).~
Deciles indexed by the max value of the bucket (e.g. "20%" includes all well sites with productivity above the tenth percentile but less than or equal to the twentieth percentile).~
Also includes finer-resolution quantiles for higher-productivity sites to improve fidelity of the distribution fit.~
Converts quantiles to sum to 1.
Definition: VAR init := (Selected_covered_we1 <= Rutherford_selected3)*Quantile_to_simulate;~
VAR initZeroToNull := IF init = 0 THEN Null ELSE init;~
Sum(Min(initZeroToNull, Quantile_to_simulate)=Quantile_to_simulate, Productivity_quantil)/Size(Productivity_quantil)
NodeLocation: 512,184,1
NodeSize: 88,40
WindState: 2,1086,412,720,350
ValueState: 2,125,2,806,424,,MIDM
NumberFormat: 2,D,6,2,0,0,6,0,$,0,"ABBREV",0,,,0,0,15,
Att__TotalsIndex: [OLD_Decile]

Variable Selected_covered_we1
Title: Selected covered well site productivity quantiles
